==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: nincompoop
<hw>nin"com*poop</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[A corruption of
<ets>non compos</ets>.]</ety> <def>A fool; a silly or stupid
person.</def> <mark>[Law]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>An old ninnyhammer, a dotard, a <qex>nincompoop</qex>, is the best
language she can afford me.</q> <rj><qau>Addison.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>nine</ent>⟦br⟧
